===Etymology===
Originally referred to a lazy person, from {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|slugge}}, probably of Scandinavian or {{etyl|non|en}} origin; compare dialectal Norwegian {{m|no|sluggje||heavy, slow person}}.

